{"by":"trwm","id":40234786,"kids":[40236439],"parent":40233232,"text":"Similar to OP if information is low density like a legal contract I can do 1200wpm after a few hours of getting used to it. Daily normal is 600wpm, if the text is heavy going enough I have to drop it down to 100 wpm and put it on loop.<p>Like usual the limit isn&#x27;t how fast human io is but how fast human processing works.","time":1714647987,"type":"comment"}
